  "logNo": "222957363696",
  "title": "[별외] QR코드 작성법 (가장 간단한 방법)",
  "addDate": "2022. 12. 17.",
  "categoryNo": "32",
  "url": "https://m.blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/222957363696",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-41989fa4-ed25-44ef-91e5-98088df64a29\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9fc9a792-d678-4d81-bcb8-36d7ae422ffb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2504de98-d2a7-4c4e-91f6-4ef18f2dd9c2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-1ac620bd-ec6a-4917-8629-9ebc45a75e1d\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>프로필이나 홍보용 이미지작업을 할때 QR코드를 사용하는 경우가 많습니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9730fd7a-cac6-4cd8-930b-65648bd0a057\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-bc36efc2-2b69-49d1-bcaf-384627f517c7\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">QR코드는 Quick Response Coded의 약자로 격자무늬 조합의 2차원 생성 코드를 말합니다. 흔히 말해 무한으로 만들 수 있는 무늬의 조합으로 네이버 QR만들기를 통해 쉽개 만들 수 있습니다. QR코드는 사이트연동은 물론 블로그나 페이스북등의 연동 기능과 바코드처럼도 활용할 수 있는 장점이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-924de2d5-236f-4a1f-8125-93223a5d0dc6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a74ddc87-798f-407c-ad1f-c9efa39bb580\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4bb30a71-5839-40bc-b6de-eb12597833c0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d09ff003-ca1d-420c-a435-fa8ff086ac04\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://terms.naver.com/alikeMeaning.naver?query=00042039\" target=\"_blank\">https://terms.naver.com/alikeMeaning.naver?query=00042039</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>  <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9f24b991-4ab5-4d57-9d53-2ec207dc5860\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5c350ee7-57b3-4aab-bccd-0bca77c3d590\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-45c91aa9-a68c-4767-95dc-41a9d38c55bb\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">오늘은 프로필명함에 사용되는 QR코드 생성에 대해 알아 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a166a0a0-0970-4132-a27c-d0886b8b6de3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-a166a0a0-0970-4132-a27c-d0886b8b6de3\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTZfMTc3/MDAxNjcxMTYwMzEzMTUz.qPZZbQzqwTWqoFk459TRKZ3e_B4MkGTNVcqti-9Akcog.EnLnjbC0ihfR-Wx0Fqq8IaAbw5becg6rBA30_AXpd1Ig.PNG.cookthedesign/%EC%9B%90%EC%B0%BD%ED%9B%88_%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1772\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2954\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTZfMTc3/MDAxNjcxMTYwMzEzMTUz.qPZZbQzqwTWqoFk459TRKZ3e_B4MkGTNVcqti-9Akcog.EnLnjbC0ihfR-Wx0Fqq8IaAbw5becg6rBA30_AXpd1Ig.PNG.cookthedesign/%EC%9B%90%EC%B0%BD%ED%9B%88_%EC%88%98%EC%A0%95.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-440ba947-adb2-4183-b044-18d3067b5672\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5f17326c-bfbe-4e17-b0d7-d580074f0380\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7492ff9b-afae-4988-8700-a2f39feaefcf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-050482e6-69bd-40be-9896-e16b3ebdfb5c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-050482e6-69bd-40be-9896-e16b3ebdfb5c\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTZfMjQ3/MDAxNjcxMTYwNjA3Njgy.OoOtce_Ln6nFhWychpBkPFqki4hFNh7qnJBIi48GwxAg.l2NfQ6gz3CPWMOpTRmV08mxW4kCFFjHWulWhT9JTVHEg.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1772\", \"originalHeight\" : \"775\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTZfMjQ3/MDAxNjcxMTYwNjA3Njgy.OoOtce_Ln6nFhWychpBkPFqki4hFNh7qnJBIi48GwxAg.l2NfQ6gz3CPWMOpTRmV08mxW4kCFFjHWulWhT9JTVHEg.PNG.cookthedesign/30_%EC%82%AC%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8%EC%84%A4%EB%AA%85_221112.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ee622df8-30cc-4940-b864-8870b12a1492\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-fd71ede2-7603-4158-b494-e7fa1d1e885d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-5448c5f0-c940-4298-a068-64d9fa0f634b\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTZfOTQg/MDAxNjcxMTYwNjcyNTAz.OK0X8784baT7IYKeG2jN1T0CeKzMaxtxguwvFvxziMAg.xexPTZDwQkFS9zQ1KLiCQTUKq8LeyMeIrvCqCZ8gpnAg.PNG.cookthedesign/s1.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"660\", \"originalHeight\" : \"237\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTZfOTQg/MDAxNjcxMTYwNjcyNTAz.OK0X8784baT7IYKeG2jN1T0CeKzMaxtxguwvFvxziMAg.xexPTZDwQkFS9zQ1KLiCQTUKq8LeyMeIrvCqCZ8gpnAg.PNG.cookthedesign/s1.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-659f790b-081e-42f7-adcf-b4b5874e4ad5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b0617fa0-43c6-4e1c-bd26-e374cf0af0cf\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>네이버 QR코드 만들기 접속</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-44deee40-057c-4419-b224-f5125934409f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cf17cd57-6d5e-4ae9-a9b1-0df45dc2d477\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">네이버에서 제공하는 QR코드 생성기를 통해 쉽게 만들 수 있습니다. 간단한 QR코드는 여러 사이트에서 만들기 프로그램을 제공하지만 네이버에서 제공하는 QR코드 만들기로 설명드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3d2b1f15-d58f-4e3b-9fb5-40340317dfb4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4f3f9dab-f871-49d0-901d-ab83c749e108\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://qr.naver.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://qr.naver.com/</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>  <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-10fd6842-a345-4d2f-8099-d33c9ea691a8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-10fd6842-a345-4d2f-8099-d33c9ea691a8\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTZfMjMy/MDAxNjcxMTYxMzY1NTA5.4usEqIuPRJ24McPjNf-A_IbewPr9VvWvlixqLE_VtSUg.BTzGp3z_zh0nOZ3bwAQBrrvTbW0_NV6hbGJf6y_SdJgg.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1920\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1030\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTZfMjMy/MDAxNjcxMTYxMzY1NTA5.4usEqIuPRJ24McPjNf-A_IbewPr9VvWvlixqLE_VtSUg.BTzGp3z_zh0nOZ3bwAQBrrvTbW0_NV6hbGJf6y_SdJgg.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d917541e-5d0e-4f42-b283-e9c82dd49452\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4084af8e-a88c-4203-b196-cfa16c9ae833\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d0895d87-cac6-4ab6-8612-3751a22ea16b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">메인화면에서 나만의 QR코드 만들기 버튼을 클릭하시면 QR코드를 생성해서 다운로드 받으실 수 있습니다. 일단 제 블로그를 연동하는 QR코드를 만들어 보겠습니다. 위 화면에서 \"나만의 QR코드 만들기\" 버튼을 클릭하십시요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1fa7aadf-ea15-4739-8f77-9665f73d69b9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c6f4124e-c6c2-4d45-93fe-fbcd793b1ab3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-2ce58f68-ee1d-4299-9896-a57a2c76d2cf\" style=\"line-height:2.1;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-be5ef916-17c4-4da8-b0f4-4f928a50d2ec\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">한 아이디에서 생성할 수 있는, 코드의 개수는 제한이 없습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-3e223e2f-68a8-456b-a471-4b706667426c\" style=\"line-height:2.1;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a1e77015-f564-4593-87db-6c44b7b80441\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">다만, QR코드는 하루에 100개까지 생성할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-12c4087c-025d-4810-b173-8fa36ec45dff\" style=\"line-height:2.1;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-47e92b01-d47e-4a7b-98c2-25a45facb00c\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b2a6e2c7-d0ee-4a4f-9bb1-e0bffd7abe7c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-left\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-b2a6e2c7-d0ee-4a4f-9bb1-e0bffd7abe7c\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTZfMjQ3/MDAxNjcxMTYxODY3MjAz.aeNaN8SarNnkRm4jj-bqtjpKGC6HGEq7IvX1T-Q48zog.bh7caU_8TPimjGeF4vW0ZVOrDO26qcUnDHfiYl09-V8g.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1920\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1030\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTZfMjQ3/MDAxNjcxMTYxODY3MjAz.aeNaN8SarNnkRm4jj-bqtjpKGC6HGEq7IvX1T-Q48zog.bh7caU_8TPimjGeF4vW0ZVOrDO26qcUnDHfiYl09-V8g.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-47ed15e5-edc9-408a-be5f-758c6bef7adf\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8a07adab-2f32-41be-b4cb-521133cf927a\" style=\"line-height:2.1;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-780c5254-ccca-45ae-8376-d3a4a3725fc5\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">가장 기본으로 만드는 방법은 기본형을 선택하고 추가옵션도 사용안함으로 비공개는 체크를 풀고 다음 단계로 넘어가는 방법입니다. 기본형으로 만들면 사각 박스는 네이버 초록색으로 바코드가 생성될 것이며 로고나 기타 문구 없이 QR코드만 생성될 것입니다. 저는 기본적으로 QR코드에 무언가 넣는것을 선호하지 않습니다. 사각형 박스만 자신의 로고색 정도로 변경하여 사용하기를 추천드립니다.  이 부분은 막 장난치듯이 해보시기 바랍니다. 여러가지 모양을 넣을 수 있고 가운데 자신의 로고도 기입 가능하며 스킨자체를 변경하실 수도 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-70b8f24c-48bc-42c6-955a-253e4f53d36b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d86b9fc8-2fe1-49a1-a2dd-027a29fd7098\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-d86b9fc8-2fe1-49a1-a2dd-027a29fd7098\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTZfMTE3/MDAxNjcxMTYyMTQzMTc4.QVwRhbFgADnegyUEDir2_80CU7y8pVWXNxdLLveJQXAg.9ReY3AXIwMwbCCPW5GtF805WBXG9bBkdY5hag3J3TQIg.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1920\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1030\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTZfMTE3/MDAxNjcxMTYyMTQzMTc4.QVwRhbFgADnegyUEDir2_80CU7y8pVWXNxdLLveJQXAg.9ReY3AXIwMwbCCPW5GtF805WBXG9bBkdY5hag3J3TQIg.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1f5940a3-86a2-4c91-adfd-d5da7416b0b3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-addec684-c881-494b-a656-e88487dcc300\" style=\"line-height:2.1;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f014e63b-43b9-46f1-828a-2d3a7377ead5\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">다음 단계로 넘어기면 본격적으로 정보를 입력하는 단계로 갑니다. 이때도 가장 쉬운 링크로 바로 이동 버튼을 눌러 보시기 바랍니다. 링크로 바로 이동 버튼은 아무런 군더더기 없이 바로 링크로 이동할 때 사용되는 버튼메뉴입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-23977ace-5136-4163-97c5-6aba6f971e78\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-23977ace-5136-4163-97c5-6aba6f971e78\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTZfOTUg/MDAxNjcxMTYyMjUyOTQ4.pJb-RGug5My-sEwyDQ8j2q4FRMtzSMmYZx3AhfTSWa4g.fC6CnSeLUCFJTL0AF2j8nGTn-dPjqtJKfrEBqkx2BJ0g.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1920\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1030\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTZfOTUg/MDAxNjcxMTYyMjUyOTQ4.pJb-RGug5My-sEwyDQ8j2q4FRMtzSMmYZx3AhfTSWa4g.fC6CnSeLUCFJTL0AF2j8nGTn-dPjqtJKfrEBqkx2BJ0g.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c6443284-d572-4b89-bf12-f5b286c979c4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-47af0ad3-7d92-4f8c-a628-158d5da55f25\" style=\"line-height:2.1;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7308afaa-855b-4930-befd-1f4122853ec4\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">웹주소 직접입력에서 제 블로그 주소를 넣고 작성완료를 누르면 QR코드가 생성되었습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b29230cc-555f-4904-b186-adc454d00b5b\" style=\"line-height:2.1;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-de5e0042-2529-426e-8b3e-4d62b834e239\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4018bcb0-4d2e-434e-97dc-0eb58182ae3f\" style=\"line-height:2.1;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5962748e-caf0-417e-b2e1-222537f994dc\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">미리보기를 누르면 모바일에서 바로 이동되는 상황을 확인하실 수 있습니다. 미리보기에서 제대로 사이트나 링크가 연결되어 표시된다면 이상없는것입니다. 하지만 연결을 거부했다거나 미리보기가 보이지 않는다면 그건 문제가 있는 QR이 생성되어 사용하실 수 없습니다. QR로 만들 수 없는 링크주소거나 하면 만들기가 거절될 수 있습니다. 링크를 확인해 보시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-385346b3-ec22-4a01-88f2-817ab60625b7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-385346b3-ec22-4a01-88f2-817ab60625b7\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTZfMyAg/MDAxNjcxMTYyNDM3OTAy.X1WES4_-0pwD1_VEENg_Vg2SNxGCklyw5O5AyVH3AjUg.AQ8cIo3FwJJjZFMP87_OpdDxb52BkcQCXIW3Y7ChSvYg.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1920\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1030\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEyMTZfMyAg/MDAxNjcxMTYyNDM3OTAy.X1WES4_-0pwD1_VEENg_Vg2SNxGCklyw5O5AyVH3AjUg.AQ8cIo3FwJJjZFMP87_OpdDxb52BkcQCXIW3Y7ChSvYg.PNG.cookthedesign/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-80ef09e4-90b1-4881-af55-0e11899e2ab5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module 